afkMessages: %1%3%1 %2person sent%2 %1%4%1 %2messages to you while you were AFK.%2
afkstr1: I'm busy right now. Please talk in a bag and when I come back you can just give me the bag!
afkstr10:
I'm away over 7 seas and 7 countries,
7 waters and 7 continents,
7 mountains and 7 hills,
7 plains and 7 mounds,
7 pools and 7 lakes,
7 springs and 7 meadows,
7 cities and 7 neighborhoods,
7 blocks and 7 houses…

Where not even your messages can reach me!
afkstr11: I'm away from the keyboard at the moment, but if you'll scream loud enough at your screen, I might just hear you.
afkstr14: Please leave a message and make me feel even more important than I already am.
afkstr15:
My Führer not here so stop writing to me,
or else you will find yourself with a screen full of your own messages.
afkstr16:
If I were here,
I'd tell you where I am.

But I'm not,
so ask me when I return…
afkstr17:
I am away!
I don't know when I'll be back!
Hopefully a few minutes from now!
afkstr18: I'm not available right now so please leave your name, number, and address and I will stalk you later.
afkstr19:
Sorry, I'm not here right now.
Feel free to talk to my userbot as long as you like.
I'll get back to you later.
afkstr2:
I'm away right now. If you need anything, leave a message after the beep:
beeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeep!
afkstr20: I bet you were expecting an away message!
afkstr21:
Life is so short, there are so many things to do…
I'm away doing one of them..
afkstr22:
I am not here right now…
but if I was…

wouldn't that be awesome?
afkstr3:
I'll be back in a few minutes and if I'm not…,
wait longer.
afkstr4: I'm not here right now, so I'm probably somewhere else.
afkstr5:
Roses are red,
Violets are blue,
Leave me a message,
And I'll get back to you.
afkstr6:
Sometimes the best things in life are worth waiting for…
I'll be right back.
afkstr7:
I'll be right back,
but if I'm not right back,
I'll be back later.
afkstr8:
If you haven't figured it out already,
I'm not here.
afkstr9: Hello, welcome to my away message, how may I ignore you today?
